Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:10.82,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. Why did you completely \Nburn our ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Have more faith in the gas stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:17.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the heat wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Use a flame, not a blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.57,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain was the thing\Nthat wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:28.25,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, this is my first time \Ngoing shopping with Tohru, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:32.81,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she's like when she's shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.02,sign_2987_12_Oborozuka_Shoppi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oborozuka Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:06.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't use the\Ndepartment store over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That place is like a castle \Nand makes me uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.18,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:20.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The white color reminds \Nme of the crusader's bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And the shopping district?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:30.58,sign_3408_19_Shop_at_your_loc,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shop at your local shopping district! \NUse your point card for savings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the guild's bazaars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:26.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:30.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So your standards are basically \Nbased on your past experiences, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.71,sign_3611_25_Toda_Fresh_Seafo,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Toda Fresh Seafood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start by buying the fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:33.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:34.96,Main,Fisher,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hey, Tohru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Mr. Toda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:37.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:39.97,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often I see you with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:40.96,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,She a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's my Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:42.81,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.10,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru-chan's funny, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:49.70,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We've got some good mackerel \Nin today. How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll take two of those \Nand two dried jack mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:53.60,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,He gave us an extra fillet of mackerel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that nice of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.47,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you friends with the fishmonger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We're not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:11.04,sign_4376_42_What_about_it__,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:07.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,When I was courteous to him he started \Nbeing nice in return, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, I think you have a tendency \Nto not understand human emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:13.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course things are different \Nwith you, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We share mutual love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.88,sign_4712_48_Tatsuda_Butchery,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuda Butchery
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.88,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tohru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.38,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it be today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.05,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw some extra in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.14,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:25.79,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.56,Main,Clothier,0000,0000,0000,,My, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.26,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the cosplay lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.23,Main-Top,Fortuneteller,0000,0000,0000,,Getting along well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:34.68,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,This dragon's better at socializing than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.93,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.55,Main-Top,FT,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Tohru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.24,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,She make talk condescendingly, calling humans
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:38.79,Main-Top,FT,0000,0000,0000,,Care to have your romantic fortune read?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.35,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,an inferior species and lesser creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:42.68,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Thank you, but I'm good on that front.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.87,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,but she's interacting \Nwith them normally enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.33,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she doesn't hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.33,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:54.27,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I hardly \Nknow anything about Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.82,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know more... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.46,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's probably best \Nnot to ask about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.22,Sweets,K,0000,0000,0000,,Homemade Western Confections\N{\fs20\c&H424DC1&}Salmandra
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.24,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's clearly a touchy topic for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we buy some dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:13.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love an eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:20.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? Eclair means \N flash of lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:20.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:25.52,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of lightning, there's the Norse\Ngod Thor... is your name related to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:31.21,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,According to my parents, it comes \Nfrom an author here in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.82,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your parents—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.04,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Purse snatcher! Someone stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, may I stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:44.31,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, can you do it without \Nexposing yourself as a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.17,Main,Thief,0000,0000,0000,,Good, now that I'm this far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:51.76,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.33,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this mean trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:15.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:18.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:19.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.10,Main,Toda,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Tohru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.74,Main,Clothier,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.83,Main-Top,Background,0000,0000,0000,,That was cool, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.22,Main-Top,Background,0000,0000,0000,,You've got quite the legs on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.25,Main-Top,Background,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.48,Main-Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sleep soundly tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I was sweating, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I should have told \Nyou to hold back more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Um, your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You want to hold hands a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:09.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.53,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't wash this hand for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,How does tail taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet and creamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Singing your own praises, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.33,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is my package here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:48.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.56,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I invited her into my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.64,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,But she's Tohru's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.36,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,She has horns and a tail, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.32,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,But Tohru's out shopping right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.11,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're having meat and potato stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.17,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,What to do about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:12.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.73,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Break up with Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.65,Main,Kobyashi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.61,Main,Kobyashi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:24.72,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you've seduced her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.87,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,With your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:26.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.54,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Cuckold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.00,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Slut in glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:33.28,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you making \Na mistake? I'm not a slu—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.14,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.72,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Break up with her! Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:39.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.14,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:44.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you cheating on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make things more \Ncomplicated! Not worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.43,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:49.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.77,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is called Kanna Kamui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.20,sign_11337_143_Kanna_Kamui,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(736,1)}Kanna Kamui
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.20,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's an acquaintance of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.74,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru went missing, \Nso I came searching for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:04.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, you need to let your friends know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm surprised you found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:11.71,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Lady Tohru breathe \Nfire on that cloudy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.56,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And I sensed your magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You were careless there, huh, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:19.79,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, why are you in such an outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.71,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Come home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.72,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I need you, Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.12,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.53,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.03,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take this seri—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.80,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:39.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.92,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you on your date at the bazaar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.41,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You were holding hands in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:45.96,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:46.91,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,On our date?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:48.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blush about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.07,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll kill you if I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.46,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.59,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.97,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:01.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You've become incredibly \Npowerless, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.84,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're the odd one, Lady Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:09.85,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,The mana purity here is too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-chan, do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,you can't get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.34,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:19.15,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's not? But you don't have \Nanywhere to stay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, look me in the eye and answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think your dead-fish eyes \Nare scary, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:30.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, please tell us honestly \Nabout what you're planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you're after Miss Kobayashi, \Nthen I'm sorry, but give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, be quiet for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.79,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.05,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You were exiled for a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna does love pulling pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so to sum things up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.32,sign_14126_193_Mommy__open_up_,ScreenLeft,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.32,sign_14126_194_I_ll_be_good_,ScreenRight,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Like that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably not allowed to return \Nuntil she reflects on her actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:56.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It would be futile for me \Nto try sending her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So right now she's all on her own...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.84,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you have no place to stay,\N want to live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:18.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You told me no the first \Ntime I asked, though. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Once you have one, two's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.59,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.34,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're plotting something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.10,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to use me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't trust anyone \Nin an unknown world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't trust anyone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:45.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Trusting someone is something that happens \Nafter you become friends or become lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-chan, I won't ask you to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.30,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:12.05,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I fell in love \Nwith Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:30.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:32.74,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:33.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.65,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Am I domesticating her with food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.97,sign_16755_222_Episode_2,K,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.97,Eyecatch,K,0000,0000,0000,,Second Dragon, Kanna! (We're Totally Spoiling Here)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.93,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.35,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What about your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.69,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna is a child, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to exercise her \Nbody to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:01.66,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid I spent my days \Nplaying video games, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:05.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, would you like to \Nplay with me outside today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.32,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come, too, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.28,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I hate exercising.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just landed in a big \Nfield that looked nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep off the \Nfatigue from my deathma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.02,sign_18014_240_Deathma__Short_f,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(528,1)}Deathma: Short for death march. \NTo work without rest under an \Noverloaded schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.02,reception,,0000,0000,0000,,No Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wake me up when you're finished playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:37.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And return us to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, shall we play by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.27,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.43,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you were going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,How can I sleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you battling to the \Ndeath over all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:23.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. We were just\N roughhousing a little bit is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.44,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're over-exaggerating, Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, I'm at the disadvantage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:29.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I bet you wanted to join in,\Ntoo, right, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're not very honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:31.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.70,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.91,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to move around in a human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:40.28,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your strength \Nwas gone, Kanna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:43.46,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,The source of my power is electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.36,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So it returned after I recharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Are you made of lithium?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If we're playing around, \Nkeep it to human standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We were at human standards, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:52.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:53.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.95,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,In our world there are plenty of \Nhumans capable of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There's very few, in fact \Nnone, who can here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, I saw some on TV the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's fiction, it wasn't reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, for crushing your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:13.15,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sleeping over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.28,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your playing around to my level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:21.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's try to recall how \NMiss Kobayashi usually acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.03,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.37,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,The power of dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:28.86,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it a few times now, \Nbut it's still terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.11,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,If they felt like it, our world would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,My lower back! My lower back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.77,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired! I'm dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:49.85,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.92,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,They'd never destroy our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.99,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,And that exhausted behavior \Nis totally me, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:01.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you really didn't want\Nto play, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.77,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we can play shiritori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:21.52,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Apple ({\i1}ringo{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.52,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Gorilla ({\i1}gorira{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Trumpet ({\i1}rappa{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Parachute ({\i1}parashuuto{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.56,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Tornado ({\i1}toruneedo{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:30.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do, do... hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dragon ({\i1}doragon{\i0})!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:33.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:48.21,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You only left my tail-meat behind again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Though if you turned it into ground \Nmeat, I probably wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But then you wouldn't know \Nit's my meat, would you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.68,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You want to emphasize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.56,sign_23115_306_The_Crane__Maide,Book,0000,0000,0000,,The Crane Repays a Debt
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:09.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, please don't peek into \Nthe kitchen until I call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.57,sign_23115_306_The_Crane__Maide - Copy,Book,0000,0000,0000,,The Crane Repays a Debt
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:10.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:12.98,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.35,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need grilled tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.57,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.14,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? To work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.56,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, you have things to do \Nwith me today, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:27.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Things to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:31.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna hasn't been in this \Nworld very long, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd teach her a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:38.77,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,No! I want to go with Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She's suddenly attached to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep being selfish, I'll break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:44.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:49.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Kanna, we're going to have you \Nlearn the commonsense of this society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.19,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Commonsense of this society?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, you should learn \Nwhat you must not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.43,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, you must honor traffic lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:00.07,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you'll be hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.42,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's what those iron boxes are called?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.38,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, you're smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.96,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,How do they move?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Probably with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:12.76,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently you need a device \Ncalled a "license" for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.43,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Does Kobayashi possess a license?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.00,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to try riding in a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:21.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to possess a license, \Nbut she doesn't have a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.32,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it imposes strains \Ncalled "vehicle inspections" or "loans."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:27.89,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I guess power comes at \Na price in every world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:32.05,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it would be really easy \Nif she had you carry her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.94,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't Kobayashi do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:39.13,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you've got another relative with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.28,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a maid, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, a Gothic lolita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,A Gothic lolita with a tribal theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.62,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, interesting tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:51.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru said she was going to teach her \Nsome things, but I'm so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.32,Main-Top,Man,0000,0000,0000,,First we should run tests using this module.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.07,Main-Top,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Mhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.88,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru-chan seems to have \Nher act together, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.48,Main-Top,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Then merge it with this one,\N and run an integration test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.77,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:18:00.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose perhaps she does have a lot \Nof compassion for her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.59,Main-Top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,For real? That can't be. That's wicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:04.30,Main-Top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:04.71,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.15,Main-Top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Magic words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:05.68,Main-Top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.68,Main-Top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can get through most conversations \Nusing them, so try to remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.81,Main-Top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,That's wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:09.85,Main-Top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,That's wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.18,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.53,sign_26235_367_In_Trouble_,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,In Trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.52,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.43,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,A tool children play with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:18.46,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,How do they play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.73,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it uses the \Nprinciple of levers, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's a training device for catapults!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.20,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:29.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is how children learn the means \Nof combating monsters in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.65,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:33.74,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,A crepe stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.47,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweet, like yatagarasu eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.59,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,An ice cream stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.02,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold. But good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.65,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,This world is peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.96,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Are there dragons in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like there aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if they went extinct \Nor if they moved elsewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.46,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Is it wrong to revert to my original form?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.38,Main-Top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's fine, it's fine, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:14.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't let your \Nform be seen, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.71,Main-Top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can you use perception blocking, Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.40,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.98,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's hardly ever \Nany need for it anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.80,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:31.15,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.87,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you had died...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.48,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So I was happy to find you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:44.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this world to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told, I was on the verge of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,but Miss Kobayashi saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.31,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to repay her by \Nbeing her maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,While letting people think I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:20:00.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've only told a handful of \Ndragons about my survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Like Miss Lucoa and Mr. Fafnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.51,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a retiree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That might be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kanna,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:20.54,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:25.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kanna, isn't there \Nmore you'd like to know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.74,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see Kobayashi's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.62,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go say hello, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I blocked perception of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.02,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.80,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:25.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's not practice for catapults?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. It's equipment kids play on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:50.03,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.03,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:54.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:27.92,Next Episode,K,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,181)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:29.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, supposedly there are\Nmyriads of gods living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:31.88,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, what does "myriads" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:34.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently gods reside in \Nall manner of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.06,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.93,sign_33949_436_Episode_3,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.93,sign_33949_437_Start_of_a_New_L,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Start of a New Life! (That Doesn't Go Well, Of Course)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:38.21,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
